```plantuml
@startuml gcba-iris_iris

actor User
participant CLI
participant Dispatcher
participant Dock
participant Handler
participant Hook
participant ThreadPool

User -> CLI: Execute command (e.g., run flow)
CLI -> Dispatcher: Initialize and load flows
Dispatcher -> Dock: Register dock instances
Dispatcher -> Handler: Register handler instances
Dispatcher -> Hook: Register hook instances
Dispatcher -> ThreadPool: Initialize thread pool

loop Message Processing
    Dock -> Dispatcher: Receive and parse message
    Dispatcher -> Hook: Pre-processing (input hook)
    Dispatcher -> Handler: Process message
    Handler -> Dispatcher: Generate response
    Dispatcher -> Hook: Post-processing (output hook)
    Dispatcher -> Dock: Send encoded response
    Dock -> ExternalSystem: Return response
end

@enduml
```